overview: CBC's Hockey Night In Canada presents Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 22! This year, Don's got all the great goals, hits, saves and bloopers from the 2009-2010 NHL Season PLUS Don takes a look back at the surprising Stanley Cup win by Chicago. All That and the best of last year's Coach's Corner. As Don says "you're gonna love it!"
tagline: Highlights from the 2009-2010 NHL season. Narrated by Don Cherry.
title: Don Cherry's Rock'em Sock'em Hockey 22
